Activate Your Reply Recommendation Model

After publishing Einsteinâ€™s replies to Quick Text, activate your model to show recommendations during chat and messaging sessions.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Einstein Reply Recommendations is included in the Einstein for Service add-on license.

To activate an Einstein Reply Recommendations model:
	* Confirm Published status in Setup
	* Click Activate

Service agents can now see recommended replies in the console.

To pause recommendations or edit published replies, see Maintain Your Recommended Replies.
